    // Section 1: Hero Narrative
    "am.hero_title": "Certified Airport Management & Ground Staff Training in Vadodara",
    "am.hero_p1": "While the cabin crew serve passengers at 35,000 feet, it is the <strong>ground staff</strong> who ensure every flight departs on time, every passenger boards safely, and every piece of luggage reaches its destination. If cabin crew are the face of an airline, ground staff are the <em>backbone</em>—the operational engine that keeps the entire aviation ecosystem running.",
    "am.hero_p2": "At <strong>Wings Institute, Vadodara</strong>—Gujarat's oldest and largest aviation training institute since 2008—we have specifically designed our <strong>Airport Management programme</strong> for candidates who seek <em>stability</em>, <em>technical skill development</em>, and <em>long-term job security</em> over the glamour of constant travel. This is a career built on logistics, security protocols, customer service excellence, and operational precision.",
    "am.who_for_title": "Who Is This Programme For?",
    "am.who_for_intro": "Our Airport Management course is ideal for:",
    "am.who_for_1": "<strong>Male candidates</strong> who may feel excluded from \"air hostess\" marketing but want aviation careers",
    "am.who_for_2": "<strong>Students seeking stability</strong> over constant travel and jet lag",
    "am.who_for_3": "<strong>Candidates who don't meet cabin crew height requirements</strong> but are passionate about aviation",
    "am.who_for_4": "<strong>Those interested in technical roles</strong> like security, cargo, ramp operations, and logistics",
    "am.who_for_5": "<strong>Aspirants who want to work near their hometown</strong>—Vadodara, Ahmedabad, Surat, or Rajkot",
    "am.hero_p3": "Unlike cabin crew positions that require specific height and have age restrictions, ground staff careers welcome candidates of all heights and offer employment well into your 50s. This is not a short-term glamour job—it is a <strong>stable, respectable career</strong> with clear progression from Customer Service Agent to Duty Manager to Airport Manager.",
    
    // Section 2: Technical Syllabus
    "am.syllabus_title": "What You Will Learn: Technical Syllabus",
    "am.syllabus_intro": "Our curriculum is designed by industry professionals who have worked at major Indian and international airports. Every module directly maps to skills tested during airline recruitment drives at <strong>Ahmedabad International Airport</strong>, <strong>Mumbai Airport</strong>, and <strong>Delhi IGI Airport</strong>.",
    "am.mod1_title_seo": "Terminal Operations & Passenger Handling",
    "am.mod1_intro": "This is the core of ground staff work—managing passenger flow from airport entry to aircraft boarding.",
    "am.mod1_item1": "<strong>DCS (Departure Control System)</strong> – Airline check-in software",
    "am.mod1_item2": "Boarding Pass & Baggage Tag Generation",
    "am.mod1_item3": "Immigration & Customs Documentation",
    "am.mod1_item4": "Boarding Gate Management & Final Calls",
    "am.mod1_item5": "Special Assistance (Wheelchair, Unaccompanied Minors)",
    "am.mod1_item6": "Flight Delay & Cancellation Handling",
    "am.mod1_item7": "<strong>Amadeus & Galileo GDS</strong> – Reservation systems",
    "am.mod1_item8": "Lounge Operations & Premium Services",
    "am.mod1_highlight": "<strong>Technical Highlight:</strong> You will receive hands-on training on mock practice softwares similar to <strong>Amadeus</strong> and <strong>Galileo</strong>—the two most widely used Global Distribution Systems (GDS) in the aviation industry. This technical skill alone makes you valuable for airline ticketing counters, travel agencies, and corporate travel desks.",
    "am.mod2_title_seo": "Ramp Services & Ground Handling",
    "am.mod2_intro": "The ramp is where the action happens—aircraft turnaround, baggage loading, and ground equipment operation. These are high-demand roles with excellent career growth.",
    "am.mod2_item1": "<strong>Aircraft Marshalling</strong> – Guiding aircraft to parking bay",
    "am.mod2_item2": "Baggage Handling & Loading Procedures",
    "am.mod2_item3": "<strong>Load & Trim Sheets</strong> – Weight & balance calculations",
