    "am.mod3_intro": "Aviation Security (AVSEC) is one of the most critical and high-paying specialisations in ground operations. This certification gives you a <strong>massive edge</strong> over other candidates.",
    "am.mod3_item1": "<strong>X-Ray Screening</strong> – Baggage & cargo scanning",
    "am.mod3_item2": "Physical Frisking & Pat-Down Procedures",
