    // Section 1: The Skill-Based Advantage
    "hm.sec1_title": "Diploma in Hotel Management & Hospitality Operations",
    "hm.sec1_p1": "Let us address the elephant in the room: the endless <strong>Degree vs Diploma</strong> debate that confuses thousands of Gujarati families every admission season. Parents worry: <em>\"Will a diploma have the same value as a degree?\"</em> Students wonder: <em>\"Should I spend 3-4 years on a BHM or complete a 1-year diploma?\"</em>",
    "hm.sec1_p2": "Here is the truth that most educational consultants won't tell you: <strong>In hospitality, skills trump theory. Every single time.</strong>",
    "hm.paradigm_title": "The Gujarat Paradigm: Faster ROI Through Focused Training",
    "hm.paradigm_intro": "Consider this scenario that plays out across Gujarat every year:",
