    "hm.sec1_closing": "At <strong>Wings Institute, Vadodara</strong>—Gujarat's oldest and largest hospitality training institute since 2008—we have spent 17 years perfecting a curriculum that delivers exactly what hotels demand. Our alumni now work at the finest properties across India, Dubai, Qatar, Singapore, and on international cruise ships.",
    
