    "hm.sec4_title": "6-Month Industrial Training: Your Gateway to Permanent Employment",
    "hm.sec4_intro": "Here is the game-changer that separates Wings Institute from every other hospitality programme: our <strong>mandatory 6-month internship</strong> in genuine 5-star properties. This is not a formality or a summer project—it is half your education.",
    "hm.intern_where": "Where Our Students Intern",
    "hm.intern_gain": "What You Gain During Internship:",
    "hm.intern1": "<strong>Paid Stipend:</strong> ₹1,500 - ₹5,000/month depending on property and location",
    "hm.intern2": "<strong>Free Meals & Accommodation:</strong> Most 5-star hotels provide staff quarters",
    "hm.intern3": "<strong>Real Work Experience:</strong> You work alongside professional staff, not in a training room",
    "hm.intern4": "<strong>Pre-Placement Offers (PPO):</strong> 60-70% of our interns receive permanent job offers from their internship hotels",
    "hm.intern5": "<strong>Industry Certification:</strong> Internship completion certificate from a recognised 5-star brand",
    "hm.intern_hidden": "<strong>The Hidden Value:</strong> Even if you don't receive a PPO, your internship experience becomes your strongest asset in interviews. When you tell a recruiter <em>\"I worked 6 months at Taj handling real guests,\"</em> it carries infinitely more weight than saying <em>\"I studied hotel management theory for 3 years.\"</em>",
    
