    "hpSeo.roi_row6_factor": "ROI Timeline",
    "hpSeo.roi_row6_wings": "Fee recovered in 3-4 months",
    "hpSeo.roi_row6_degree": "Fee recovered in 12-18 months",
    "hpSeo.roi_p2": "Consider this: A student who joins Wings at age 17 after 12th std can be earning ₹35,000-45,000/month by age 18. By the time their peers finish a 3-year BBA, our alumni have already accumulated 2 years of salary + work experience + promotions. This isn't anti-degree rhetoric—it's simple mathematics favoured by pragmatic Gujarati families.",
    
    // Section 4: Courses
    "hpSeo.courses_title": "Industry-Integrated Vocational Courses",
    "hpSeo.courses_p1": "Wings Institute offers five core verticals, each designed with direct input from hiring managers at airlines, airports, and hotels. Our curriculum isn't theoretical—it's reverse-engineered from actual interview rubrics and job requirements.",
    "hpSeo.course_ah_title": "Air Hostess & Cabin Crew",
    "hpSeo.course_ah_desc": "Train on our Airbus A330 mock cabin. Master safety drills (Evacuation, Fire Fighting), meal service, grooming, and aviation English. Placement with IndiGo, Vistara, Air India, Emirates, Qatar Airways.",
    "hpSeo.course_ah_btn": "Explore Course",
    "hpSeo.course_am_title": "Airport Management & Ground Staff",
    "hpSeo.course_am_desc": "Learn Amadeus & Galileo GDS, DCS check-in systems, AVSEC (Aviation Security), Dangerous Goods Regulations (DGR), ramp operations, and cargo handling. Placement at major Indian airports.",
    "hpSeo.course_am_btn": "Explore Course",
    "hpSeo.course_hm_title": "Diploma in Hotel Management",
    "hpSeo.course_hm_desc": "Comprehensive hospitality training: F&B Service (fine-dine etiquette, mixology), Front Office (PMS software, night audit), Housekeeping, and mandatory 6-month internship at 5-star properties.",
    "hpSeo.course_hm_btn": "Explore Course",
    "hpSeo.course_cu_title": "Culinary Arts & Chef Course",
    "hpSeo.course_cu_desc": "Professional chef training in our commercial kitchen. Master knife skills (Julienne, Brunoise), Indian regional cuisines, Continental (Mother sauces), and Bakery & Confectionery. HACCP food safety certification.",
    "hpSeo.course_cu_btn": "Explore Course",
    "hpSeo.course_tt_title": "Travel & Tourism Management",
    "hpSeo.course_tt_desc": "For the entrepreneurial Gujarati spirit: Learn Amadeus/Galileo GDS ticketing, visa processing, tour packaging, itinerary planning, and passport regulations. Many alumni run their own travel agencies and visa consultancies.",
    "hpSeo.course_tt_btn": "Explore Course",
    
