    "hpSeo.faq_title": "Frequently Asked Questions about Wings Institute",
    
    // FAQ Data (English)
    "hpSeo.faq1_q": "Where is Wings Institute located in Vadodara?",
    "hpSeo.faq1_a": "Wings Institute is located at 2nd floor, RG Square 14, Nutan Bharat Society, Alkapuri, Vadodara 390007, Gujarat, India. We are easily accessible from the Vadodara Railway Station (4 km) and Harni Airport (8 km). The Alkapuri area is one of Vadodara's most prestigious localities. Our opening hours are Monday to Saturday, 10:00 AM to 7:00 PM.",
    "hpSeo.faq2_q": "Does Wings Institute provide a job guarantee?",
    "hpSeo.faq2_a": "No ethical institute can legally 'guarantee' a job. Wings Institute provides 100% Placement Assistance, which means: professional resume building, unlimited mock interviews, direct referrals to our airline and hotel partners, interview calendar management, and career counselling until you are placed. Our alumni network spans Qatar Airways, Emirates, IndiGo, Singapore Airlines, Taj Hotels, Marriott, and more.",
    "hpSeo.faq3_q": "What is the fee structure for the Air Hostess course at Wings Institute?",
    "hpSeo.faq3_a": "Our Air Hostess/Cabin Crew course fees are structured to offer maximum value. The fee includes: training on our Airbus A330 mock cabin, grooming sessions, spoken English certification, safety drills, interview preparation, and placement assistance. We offer flexible installment plans and merit-based scholarships. Contact our admissions counsellor at +91-8758754444 for the current fee structure.",
    "hpSeo.faq4_q": "What makes Wings Institute different from other aviation academies in Gujarat?",
    "hpSeo.faq4_a": "Wings Institute is Gujarat's oldest and largest aviation training institute (est. 2008). Our key differentiators: 1) In-house Airbus A330 Mock Cabin - the only one in Gujarat, 2) Commercial Kitchen & Fine-dine Restaurant for hospitality training, 3) 17+ years of placement track record with international airlines, 4) Faculty comprising ex-airline crew and hotel professionals, 5) NSDC-aligned curriculum.",
    "hpSeo.faq5_q": "Can I join Wings Institute after completing 12th from Gujarati medium?",
    "hpSeo.faq5_a": "Absolutely! Over 70% of our successful alumni came from vernacular (Gujarati/Hindi medium) backgrounds. Our 'Spoken English & Communication' module is specifically designed for vernacular students. We use immersive techniques, daily practice sessions, and confidence-building exercises to transform you into a fluent English speaker within the course duration.",
    
    // Vernacular FAQs (Gujlish)
    "hpSeo.faq6_q": "Wings Institute kya che Vadodara ma?",
    "hpSeo.faq6_a": "Wings Institute Alkapuri ma che - RG Square, 2nd floor, Nutan Bharat Society, Vadodara 390007. Railway Station thi 4 km, Harni Airport thi 8 km. Alkapuri Vadodara nu best locality che. Timing: Monday-Saturday 10 AM to 7 PM. Google Maps par 'Wings Institute Vadodara' search karjo - direct directions malse!",
    "hpSeo.faq7_q": "Wings Institute ma fees ketli che?",
    "hpSeo.faq7_a": "Course par depend kare: Air Hostess ~₹1,30,000, Airport Management ~₹1,18,000, Hotel Management ~₹84,000, Culinary ~₹84,000, Travel Tourism ~₹66,000. EMI option available - 3-6 installments. Merit scholarship thi 30% sudhi discount. Exact fees mate +91-8758754444 par call karo.",
    "hpSeo.faq8_q": "Placement male ke nai Wings ma?",
    "hpSeo.faq8_a": "100% Placement ASSISTANCE aapiye - guarantee koi nathi aapi shaktu legally. Pan Wings record che: unlimited interviews jya sudhi place nai thao, direct referrals to airline/hotel partners, resume building, mock interviews. Alumni Qatar Airways, Emirates, Singapore Airlines, IndiGo, Taj Hotels ma che!",
    "hpSeo.faq9_q": "Wings Institute Gujarat ma best kyun che?",
    "hpSeo.faq9_a": "5 reasons: 1) Gujarat ma ONLY Airbus A330 Mock Cabin amari paase, 2) Commercial Kitchen + Mock Restaurant hospitality mate, 3) 17+ years experience (since 2008), 4) Ex-airline crew faculty, 5) International airline placements - Qatar, Emirates, Singapore. Google Reviews: 4.7 stars! Visit karjo - dekhai jaase.",
    "hpSeo.faq10_q": "Gujarati medium thi aviation career bani shake?",
    "hpSeo.faq10_a": "100% bani shake! 70%+ Wings students Gujarati/Hindi medium thi aave che. Special Cambridge Spoken English module che - basics thi shikhvay. Daily practice, confidence building, vocabulary - 12 months ma fluent English speaker! Qatar Airways ma fly karta alumni pan originally Gujarati medium hata.",
    "hpSeo.faq11_q": "Wings Institute ma admission kai rite levu?",
    "hpSeo.faq11_a": "Simple process: 1) Campus visit ya call +91-8758754444, 2) Free career counselling, 3) Documents: 10th, 12th marksheets, ID proof, 4) Fee payment (full ya EMI), 5) Next batch ma classes start. Walk-in welcome - Alkapuri campus, Mon-Sat 10-7. Online enquiry form pan available website par.",
    "hpSeo.faq12_q": "Wings Institute timing su che? Kya che address?",
    "hpSeo.faq12_a": "Address: 2nd Floor, RG Square 14, Nutan Bharat Society, Alkapuri, Vadodara 390007. Timing: Monday thi Saturday, 10:00 AM thi 7:00 PM. Sunday closed. Classes part-time hoy - daily 4 hours. Working students/college students mate convenient timing adjust thai shake.",
    "hpSeo.faq13_q": "Air hostess course che ke nai Wings ma?",
    "hpSeo.faq13_a": "Haan! Wings Institute BEST air hostess training aape Gujarat ma. 12 months course che: Airbus A330 mock cabin training, safety drills, grooming, spoken English, interview preparation. Only institute Gujarat ma with real aircraft mock cabin. Placements: IndiGo, SpiceJet, Air India, Emirates, Qatar Airways.",
    "hpSeo.faq14_q": "Hotel management course che Wings ma?",
    "hpSeo.faq14_a": "Haan! 12 months Hotel Management diploma - 6 months classroom + 6 months paid internship at Taj, Marriott, Hyatt. Mock restaurant, commercial kitchen, front office lab - industry-grade infrastructure. Course fees ~₹84,000. Internship ma ₹5,000-12,000/month stipend male!",
    "hpSeo.faq15_q": "Wings Institute reviews keva che?",
    "hpSeo.faq15_a": "Google Reviews: 4.7 stars! Students ane parents positive feedback aape: professional training, actual placement, supportive faculty. YouTube par alumni success stories jovani - Qatar Airways, Emirates, Singapore Airlines, Taj Hotels ma working. Visit karjo campus - current students saathe vaat karo!",
    
